        h2.description__title.c-title.c-title--small.wow.animate__animated.animate__fadeInUp What are the Benefits of a Facelift?
        p.description__desc.c-desc.wow.animate__animated.animate__fadeInUp A facelift can be a life-changing procedure. The benefits are immediate and the results can increase self-confidence, restoring a youthful appearance that has diminished with age. Below, we’ve highlighted more benefits:

