          div.wow.animate__animated.animate__fadeInUp
            .method__box
              p A facelift can eliminate excess fat
          div.wow.animate__animated.animate__fadeInUp
            .method__box
              p The procedure can reduce or even eliminate creases around the mouth, nose, and eyes
          div.wow.animate__animated.animate__fadeInUp
            .method__box
