        p.description__desc.c-desc.wow.animate__animated.animate__fadeInUp Dr. Hubert takes great care to avoid the “over-pulled” look that you sometimes see in tabloid photos.
        p.description__desc.c-desc.wow.animate__animated.animate__fadeInUp While a facelift takes an expert surgeon to provide the best results and can be a delicate surgery, we’ve provided a synopsis of Dr. Hubert’s process:

